## Core Principles

1. **Atomic notes** — one idea per note, linked to related concepts
2. **Progressive formalization** — seeds capture, saplings develop, evergreens solidify
3. **Bidirectional linking** — connections go both ways; isolated notes lose value
4. **Tag taxonomy** — `domain/scope` pattern keeps tags navigable at scale
5. **Evidence-based promotion** — status upgrades require demonstrated quality

